[normal](b)
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]order
[normal] the respondent to pay compensation to the complainant;
[normal](c) 
[normal]make
[normal] an 
[normal]appropriate recommendation
[normal](3) An 
[normal]appropriate recommendation
[normal] is a recommendation that within a specified period the respondent takes specified steps for the purpose of obviating or reducing the adverse effect of any matter to which the proceedings relate—
[normal](a) 
[normal]on
